msgid ""
"Click the *Other Node* button to create an :ref:`AudioStreamPlayer "
"<class_AudioStreamPlayer>` and rename it to ``MusicPlayer``."
msgstr ""
"*다른 노드* 버튼을 클릭하여 :ref:`AudioStreamPlayer "
